<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-15576] CQLSH missing virtual keyspaces on DESCRIBE call</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15576</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;cqlsh is missing virtual keyspaces. This patch fixes it. It also adds a dtest to avoid future regressions. &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/dineshjoshi/cassandra/tree/fix-missing-keyspace-issue-cqlsh&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Branch&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/dineshjoshi/cassandra-dtest-1/tree/fix-missing-keyspace-issue-cqlsh&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;DTests&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&#160;and &lt;a href=&quot;https://circleci.com/workflow-run/b978fe37-98a8-482b-89bf-f7b6c8c41a40&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13285882">CASSANDRA-15576</key>
